data.description: Schedule your appointment today to see this 3 year old 4 Bedroom  home located  in the heart of the city of Maryville.  This Split bedroom floor plan offers privacy in this home. Bedrooms are spacious with walk in closets.  The  primary suite has not one but two walk in closets. Home has custom trey ceilings. Hardwood and tile floors throughout.  Kitchen has wood cabinets, granite counters and a large island. You will get a formal dining area, and the guest bathroom has been upgraded with a large whirlpool  tub.  This property backs up to private woods of Maryville College and is professionally landscaped with hand selected trees that will bloom beautifully in the Spring and will pop in the Fall.  Added storage under the deck and don't forget you get MARYVILLE CITY SCHOOLS!
